rComments: Professor Obradovic may be the best professor I have had at university. She is tough and uncompromising in what she expects from her students, which makes succeeding in her course all the more rewarding. If you want a professor who actually cares, not only about the course material, but about you and your ideas, Professor Obradovic is a perfect fit

Prof. Obradovic is wonderful! She is very helpful, considerate and passionate. She'll make you work for your grades... but you learn so much in her classes that you don't even realize how much you've absorbed by the end! She's super knowledgeable and young - U of T needs more professors like her!
Best prof at UofT by far! Incredibly knowledgeable, enthusiastic and approachable. Highly recommend taking any of her classes.
Was surprised at the level of knowledge she has at such a young age. The level of analysis she presents on topics is phenomenal

Prof. Obradovic is wonderful; a great lecturer and good at facilitating discussion. Also completely approachable and very very helpful. She's incredibly enthusiastic about her course material, which makes her classes fun!
Prof. Obradovic is a great lecturer, and also very open to class discussion. recommended
Really, really smart prof. I don't know how she does it, but prof Obradovic is a superwoman!
